            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "In Shiksha Bharti Public School I am not working as a professional but I am also growing as an individual.\nThe school provides a joyful learning environment which provides the intellectual, social and emotional growth of students.The school administration works hand in hand with the parents and with the other staff members catering to the needs of the students.The school prepare children to face the challenges of life with confidence, imagination and integrity. SBPS also partner with families to bring out the best in every child. The school is committed in creating an environment where children acquire wisdom, lead lives of personal honour, embrace diversity, appreciate beauty, pursue physical well-being and act with generosity and compassion.\nAs a co-ordinator I am very happy with the pedagogy adopted by the school.The safe and the healthy environment provided in the school has made it a second home for me.",
